title: 1996 Philippine Sangguniang Kabataan election
text:
<a href="Sangguiniang%20Kabataan">Sangguiniang Kabataan</a> elections were held on May 6, 1996. The <a href="Sangguniang%20Kabataan">Sangguniang Kabataan</a> (SK) (Youth Council) is the governing body in every chapter of the "Katipunan ng Kabataan" (Youth Federation). Each "<a href="barangay">barangay</a>" in the <a href="Philippines">Philippines</a> is mandated by law to have its own chapter of the Katipunan ng Kabataan in which the members elect their officers called as the Sangguniang Kabataan. The Sangguniang Kabataan is the youth <a href="legislature">legislature</a> in every local village or community.
